snippet.title: WrestleQuest - Announcement Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
WrestleQuest is coming to Nintendo Switch May 2023! Wishlist today: https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/wrestlequest-switch/

Pro wrestling and RPG fantasy collide in the ultimate pixel powered adventure. “Macho Man” Randy Savage and tons of other icons offer guidance as you powerbomb your way to glory beyond the ring. This hero’s journey ain’t just an epic quest, it’s WRESTLEQUEST!

#WrestleQuest #IndieWorld #NintendoSwitch

Subscribe for more Nintendo fun! https://goo.gl/HYYsot
